item.description:
@exe626 wrote:

ILLEGAL? everything is illegal on that damn website I swear. If he would have just said nothing he would have been fine ;
Btw, don’t double post.

[quote=“xxlegitxx”]*****
If, acting reasonably, we consider that our terms and conditions have or may have been breached, or that it is necessary in order to prevent or stop any harm or damage to us, the Game, other players or the general public or to minimize our liability to others, we reserve the right with or without prior notice to (amongst other things): Terminate (as defined above) or modify any or all accounts of the Game (or any of our other games) which we think are connected with you and/or otherwise block your access to our websites and services and take such other steps as we consider reasonable.

They can’t simply ban you for no reason, though they do quite frequently (e.g., I was given blackmarks for absolutely no reason, and if a human actually read my response, they’d fix it. But apparently $60 a year isn’t enough to pay for decent customer support.). As I’m perusing this thread, I am reaching full awareness of how much lies Tropicsun is spewing from both ends of his body.

“you will get banned alex, the agreement between mopar and jagex was that the site could remain up but playing it was illegal!!!”

Yes, and you know of this ‘agreement,’ how? And why would they reach an agreement? If it was clearly illegal, why couldn’t Jagex simply sue to put it down? Two possibilities: a) Jagex doesn’t care. b) They don’t have full proof that it was illegal.

Both of those reasons don’t side well with you. By the way, don’t insult our intelligence even more by posting. We are not as inept as you seem to think we are; we have more sense than to believe you. Don’t deny it… you’ll only fool your five-year-old peers.

EDIT: By the way, Skull, Moparscape does not connect directly to RS worlds, access any information between the applet and an RS world, generate input to RS, does not display content from RS website, contain adverts/links, or the majority of whatever else you posted.[/quote]Runscape forums as a whole just got pwnd so hard its insane.
